{"tid":98611,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國一架艦載固定翼預警機曝光","createTime":"2017-01-28T14:01:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-30T13:23:34.000Z","uid":58099,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0f8f63cff74980335b313e8bbf60cbc4556d3847","tid":98611,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T14:01:38.000Z","msg":"年初一，一張疑似中國艦載固定翼預警機的照片在網上曝光！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/28/215517_d007c2eadcbac52418e9217237544c66.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F28%2F215517_d007c2eadcbac52418e9217237544c66.jpg&h=d5d10c3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n從照片上看，拍攝地點是我軍航母陸上模擬場地，因此很可能這是中國艦載預警機訓練使用的模型。從外觀上看，與美國E-2預警機、蘇聯雅克-44等經典設計相似。<br />\n<br />\n由於艦載固定翼預警機重量大，需要配合彈射裝置起飛，因此，預計會在002航母上首次啓用。"},{"pid":"791491b0e8d9e9aeab5f80d0ca12de512e4c9ebc","tid":98611,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T14:43:47.000Z","msg":"又抄人外型，但入面空心<br />\n之後搵人扮比人偷拍到。<br />\n<br />\n垃圾支那軍備，你問我答"},{"pid":"5f19a502929738a7a8b7274d0378104f12f8e9a7","tid":98611,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T17:30:26.000Z","msg":"1:1模型機係YOUTUBE大把啦<br />\n<br />\n放個模型, 你條支那賤畜就打晒飛機?<br />\n<br />\n飛得起先講啦"},{"pid":"c6098289c442aeb57f56ff5da5fe40a92f92c3d2","tid":98611,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T05:27:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1:1模型機係YOUTUBE大把啦<br />\n<br />\n放個模型, 你條支那賤畜就打晒飛機?<br />\n<br />\n飛得起先講啦</blockquote><br />\n佢j20 都未試過表演快飛"},{"pid":"bb7d5a81393cc00abc6f62bdbdaf532a7c1a090d","tid":98611,"uid":52943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T05:48:29.000Z","msg":"渦輪螺旋槳引擎識得做未?又同惠普買呀?"},{"pid":"652bc8b3e5beb919e813dfd66c523edc9d0132b5","tid":98611,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T10:29:08.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"08bd4f6978f40692bcb2c82ef4f4b61a5b955805","tid":98611